{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"3f8d0c29-4be4-4d09-a0a9-dd1a7e29b386","content":"Yes, these are known **runtime behavioral changes in MSTest v4** — compilation succeeds but behavior differs:\n\n## 1. `TestContext.TestName` in `[ClassInitialize]`\n\nIn v4, the `TestContext` passed to `[ClassInitialize]` is a **class-level context** — it no longer has a meaningful `TestName` (it's `null`). Previously it reflected the first test's name. This is by design since class init runs once for the class, not for any specific test.\n\n**Fix:** Don't access `TestContext.TestName` in `ClassInitialize`. Use it only in test methods or `[TestInitialize]`:\n\n```csharp\n[ClassInitialize]\npublic static void ClassSetup(TestContext context)\n{\n    // context.TestName is null in v4 — use context.FullyQualifiedTestClassName instead\n    var className = context.FullyQualifiedTestClassName;\n    System.Console.WriteLine($\"Setting up class: {className}\");\n}\n```\n\n## 2. Discovery errors\n\nIn MSTest v4, **test discovery became stricter**. Common causes:\n\n- The `TestContext` property must have a **`set` accessor** (yours has it ✓), but in v4 it should also be nullable or use `required`:\n  ```csharp\n  public TestContext? TestContext { get; set; }\n  ```\n- Any exception thrown during `[ClassInitialize]` (like your `TestName` null-ref) **causes all tests in that class to fail at discovery/setup**, which surfaces as \"discovery errors\" in the test output.\n\n**Your root cause is likely #2 — the crash in `ClassSetup` cascades into discovery failures for the class.**\n\n## Fix\n\n```csharp\n[ClassInitialize]\npublic static void ClassSetup(TestContext context)\n{\n    // In v4, TestName is null in class-level context\n    var className = context.FullyQualifiedTestClassName;\n    System.Console.WriteLine($\"Setting up class: {className}\");\n}\n```\n\nWould you like me to apply this fix to your file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"bea974a9-fc42-468c-bf52-a95c3699f741","outputTokens":501,"requestId":"981A:23633C:13D2ECE:18E9B9C:69FFF96B"},"id":"6f2b9a33-d901-4bca-bea8-8c0eba37f766","timestamp":"2026-05-10T03:20:23.159Z","parentId":"1cf9e44f-a387-4894-a391-8f477b2d7763"}
